## SECTION 1: COMPLETE WORKFLOW (High Level)

```
MANUFACTURER CREATES BATCH
    â†“ (Block #1: BatchCreated)
    â†“
MANUFACTURER ASSIGNS TO DISTRIBUTOR
    â†“ (Block #2: BatchTransferred)
    â†“
DISTRIBUTOR ACCEPTS BATCH
    â†“ (Block #3: DistributorAcceptedBatch)
    â†“
DISTRIBUTOR CREATES SHIPMENT & HIRES TRANSPORTER
    â†“ (Block #4: ShipmentCreatedByDistributor)
    â†“
TRANSPORTER PICKS UP SHIPMENT
    â†“ (Block #5: TransportPickupConfirmedByTransporter)
    â†“
TRANSPORTER LOGS TEMPERATURE (Every 4 hours)
    â†“ (Blocks #6, #7, #8... TemperatureLoggedByTransporter)
    â†“
TRANSPORTER DELIVERS TO PHARMACY
    â†“ (Block #9: TransportDeliveryCompletedByTransporter)
    â†“
PHARMACY ACCEPTS DELIVERY
    â†“ (Block #10: PharmacyAcceptedDeliveryFromDistributor)
    â†“ â­ OWNERSHIP TRANSFERRED: Distributor â†’ Pharmacy
    â†“
PHARMACY DISPENSES TO PATIENT
    â†“ (Block #11: DispensingEventToPatient)
    â†“
CUSTOMER SCANS QR CODE (NO LOGIN REQUIRED)
    â†“
SEES COMPLETE BLOCKCHAIN JOURNEY
    â†“
âœ… AUTHENTICITY BADGE: GENUINE PRODUCT VERIFIED
```

