## SECTION 6: USER WORKFLOWS BY ROLE

### MANUFACTURER WORKFLOW:
```
Login â†’ Create Batch â†’ Assign to Distributor â†’ Track Progress
â”œâ”€ Form: Product name, qty, expiry
â”œâ”€ Backend: Generates QR codes, creates Block #1
â”œâ”€ Frontend: Shows batch created âœ“
â””â”€ Next: Wait for distributor to accept
```

### DISTRIBUTOR WORKFLOW:
```
Login â†’ Accept Batch â†’ Create Shipment â†’ Monitor Transit
â”œâ”€ Check: QC checklist, receipt upload, signature
â”œâ”€ Backend: Creates Block #3, updates inventory
â”œâ”€ Frontend: Batch moves to warehouse inventory
â”œâ”€ Create: Select transporter, vehicle, driver
â”œâ”€ Backend: Creates Block #4, notifies transporter
â””â”€ Monitor: Real-time GPS, temperature alerts
```

### TRANSPORTER WORKFLOW:
```
Login â†’ Pickup Shipment â†’ Log Temperature â†’ Deliver
â”œâ”€ Verify: QR codes, seals, weight (Block #5)
â”œâ”€ Transport: Every 4 hours log temperature (Blocks #6+)
â”œâ”€ Arrive: Confirm delivery to pharmacy (Block #7)
â””â”€ Next: Wait for pharmacy to accept ownership
```

### PHARMACY WORKFLOW:
```
Login â†’ Receive Alert â†’ Accept Delivery â†’ Dispense
â”œâ”€ Review: Pre-delivery report (all blocks visible)
â”œâ”€ Verify: Physical inspection checklist
â”œâ”€ Accept: Digital signature, receipt upload
â”œâ”€ Backend: Creates Block #10, ownership transferred â­
â”œâ”€ Inventory: Batch now in pharmacy stock
â”œâ”€ Dispense: Search batch, dispense units (Block #11)
â””â”€ Receipt: QR code generated for patient
```

### PUBLIC VERIFICATION WORKFLOW:
```
Scan QR Code (NO LOGIN)
    â†“
See Product Details:
â”œâ”€ Medicine name
â”œâ”€ Batch ID
â”œâ”€ Manufacturer
â”œâ”€ Expiry date âœ“
â”œâ”€ Manufacturing date
â””â”€ Current validity: 16/365 days left
    â†“
See Complete Blockchain Journey:
â”œâ”€ Block #1: Created at Cipla âœ“
â”œâ”€ Block #2: Assigned to MotilalOswal âœ“
â”œâ”€ Block #3: Accepted by MotilalOswal âœ“
â”œâ”€ Block #4: Shipped via FastHaul âœ“
â”œâ”€ Blocks #5-7: Temperature logs (all safe) âœ“
â”œâ”€ Block #8: Delivered to pharmacy âœ“
â”œâ”€ Block #9: Accepted by pharmacy âœ“
â””â”€ Block #10: Dispensed to you âœ“
    â†“
âœ… AUTHENTICITY BADGE: 100% GENUINE
â””â”€ "No tampering detected. Safe to use."
