## SECTION 9: KEY DIFFERENCES: TRADITIONAL VS BLOCKCHAIN

### TRADITIONAL SUPPLY CHAIN:
```
Manufacturer â†’ Distributor (paper/excel) â†’ Transporter (phone call)
    â†“
âŒ Easy to forge records
âŒ Can't verify authenticity easily
âŒ Disputes hard to resolve
âŒ No real-time tracking
âŒ Manual paperwork
âŒ Centralized control
```

### VERIFYCHIAN (BLOCKCHAIN):
```
Manufacturer â†’ Distributor (Block #1-3) â†’ Transporter (Block #4-8)
    â†“
âœ… Immutable records
âœ… Instant verification via QR code
âœ… Disputes resolved via blockchain proof
âœ… Real-time GPS + temperature tracking
âœ… Zero paperwork (all digital)
âœ… Decentralized & transparent
âœ… Customer trust restored
```

